{
  "video_id": "kdqUhTnAgJU",
  "title": "How the US government spies on people who protest -- including you | Jennifer Granick",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12653.0,
      "end_time": 14780.0,
      "text": "We are all activists now."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15420.0,
      "end_time": 16716.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16740.0,
      "end_time": 17939.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18500.0,
      "end_time": 19836.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll just stop here."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 19859.0,
      "end_time": 21360.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 21600.0,
      "end_time": 25740.0,
      "text": "From the families who are fighting to maintain funding for public schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26460.0,
      "end_time": 30836.0,
      "text": "the tens of thousands of people who joined Occupy Wall Street"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30860.0,
      "end_time": 33360.0,
      "text": "or marched with Black Lives Matter"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33600.0,
      "end_time": 36620.0,
      "text": "to protest police brutality against African Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37580.0,
      "end_time": 40760.0,
      "text": "families that join rallies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40100.0,
      "end_time": 42100.0,
      "text": "pro-life and pro-choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43420.0,
      "end_time": 45156.0,
      "text": "those of us who are afraid"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45180.0,
      "end_time": 48556.0,
      "text": "that our friends and neighbors are going to be deported"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48580.0,
      "end_time": 50556.0,
      "text": "or that they&#39;ll be added to lists"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50580.0,
      "end_time": 51900.0,
      "text": "because they are Muslim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53300.0,
      "end_time": 57540.0,
      "text": "people who advocate for gun rights and for gun control"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58460.0,
      "end_time": 61956.0,
      "text": "and the millions of people who joined the women&#39;s marches"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61980.0,
      "end_time": 64756.0,
      "text": "all across the country this last January."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64780.0,
      "end_time": 67436.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67460.0,
      "end_time": 69556.0,
      "text": "We are all activists now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69580.0,
      "end_time": 74600.0,
      "text": "and that means that we all have something to worry about from surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75140.0,
      "end_time": 77836.0,
      "text": "Surveillance means government collection and use"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77860.0,
      "end_time": 81760.0,
      "text": "of private and sensitive data about us."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81100.0,
      "end_time": 83360.0,
      "text": "And surveillance is essential"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83600.0,
      "end_time": 86156.0,
      "text": "to law enforcement and to national security."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86180.0,
      "end_time": 88156.0,
      "text": "But the history of surveillance"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88180.0,
      "end_time": 91676.0,
      "text": "is one that includes surveillance abuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91700.0,
      "end_time": 95156.0,
      "text": "where this sensitive information has been used against people"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95180.0,
      "end_time": 96716.0,
      "text": "because of their race,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96740.0,
      "end_time": 98515.0,
      "text": "their national origin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98540.0,
      "end_time": 100596.0,
      "text": "their sexual orientation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100620.0,
      "end_time": 103796.0,
      "text": "and in particular, because of their activism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 103820.0,
      "end_time": 105419.0,
      "text": "their political beliefs."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106580.0,
      "end_time": 109196.0,
      "text": "About 53 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109220.0,
      "end_time": 112756.0,
      "text": "Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. gave his \"I have a dream\" speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112780.0,
      "end_time": 114600.0,
      "text": "on the Mall in Washington."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114860.0,
      "end_time": 119556.0,
      "text": "And today the ideas behind this speech of racial equality and tolerance"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 119580.0,
      "end_time": 121515.0,
      "text": "are so noncontroversial"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121540.0,
      "end_time": 124220.0,
      "text": "that my daughters study the speech in third grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124980.0,
      "end_time": 126316.0,
      "text": "But at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126340.0,
      "end_time": 128740.0,
      "text": "Dr. King was extremely controversial."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 129340.0,
      "end_time": 134836.0,
      "text": "The legendary and notorious FBI Director J. Edgar Hoover believed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 134860.0,
      "end_time": 136676.0,
      "text": "or wanted to believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136700.0,
      "end_time": 140274.0,
      "text": "that the Civil Rights Movement was a Soviet communist plot"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 140299.0,
      "end_time": 143460.0,
      "text": "intended to destabilize the American government."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 143900.0,
      "end_time": 150156.0,
      "text": "And so Hoover had his agents put bugs in Dr. King&#39;s hotel rooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150180.0,
      "end_time": 155716.0,
      "text": "and those bugs picked up conversations between civil rights leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155740.0,
      "end_time": 160180.0,
      "text": "talking about the strategies and tactics of the Civil Rights Movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 160900.0,
      "end_time": 163116.0,
      "text": "They also picked up sounds of Dr. King"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163140.0,
      "end_time": 165995.0,
      "text": "having sex with women who were not his wife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 166200.0,
      "end_time": 168756.0,
      "text": "and J. Edgar Hoover saw the opportunity here"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168780.0,
      "end_time": 172420.0,
      "text": "to discredit and undermine the Civil Rights Movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173220.0,
      "end_time": 176836.0,
      "text": "The FBI sent a package of these recordings"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176860.0,
      "end_time": 179940.0,
      "text": "along with a handwritten note to Dr. King,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180700.0,
      "end_time": 186380.0,
      "text": "and a draft of this note was found in FBI archives years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 187100.0,
      "end_time": 188835.0,
      "text": "and the letter said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188860.0,
      "end_time": 191636.0,
      "text": "\"You are no clergyman and you know it."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 191660.0,
      "end_time": 195220.0,
      "text": "King, like all frauds, your end is approaching.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195860.0,
      "end_time": 200700.0,
      "text": "The letter even seemed to encourage Dr. King to commit suicide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201380.0,
      "end_time": 205156.0,
      "text": "saying, \"King, there is only one thing left for you to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 205180.0,
      "end_time": 206756.0,
      "text": "You know what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206780.0,
      "end_time": 211116.0,
      "text": "You better take it before your filthy, abnormal, fraudulent self"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211140.0,
      "end_time": 212995.0,
      "text": "is bared to the nation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 213200.0,
      "end_time": 214436.0,
      "text": "But the important thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214460.0,
      "end_time": 216140.0,
      "text": "Dr. King was not abnormal."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216700.0,
      "end_time": 220859.0,
      "text": "Every one of us has something that we want to hide from somebody."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 221820.0,
      "end_time": 223636.0,
      "text": "And even more important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 223660.0,
      "end_time": 226140.0,
      "text": "J. Edgar Hoover wasn&#39;t abnormal either."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226900.0,
      "end_time": 228836.0,
      "text": "The history of surveillance abuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 228860.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "is not the history of one bad, megalomaniacal man."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232900.0,
      "end_time": 235916.0,
      "text": "Throughout his decades at the FBI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235940.0,
      "end_time": 239676.0,
      "text": "J. Edgar Hoover enjoyed the support of the presidents that he served,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 239700.0,
      "end_time": 241980.0,
      "text": "Democratic and Republican alike."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 242500.0,
      "end_time": 245836.0,
      "text": "After all, it was John F. Kennedy and his brother Robert Kennedy"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245860.0,
      "end_time": 248820.0,
      "text": "who knew about and approved the surveillance of Dr. King."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 250460.0,
      "end_time": 254876.0,
      "text": "Hoover ran a program called COINTELPRO for 15 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 254900.0,
      "end_time": 259676.0,
      "text": "which was designed to spy on and undermine civic groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 259700.0,
      "end_time": 262436.0,
      "text": "that were devoted to things like civil rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 262460.0,
      "end_time": 264195.0,
      "text": "the Women&#39;s Rights Movement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264220.0,
      "end_time": 266956.0,
      "text": "and peace groups and anti-war movements."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 266980.0,
      "end_time": 269339.0,
      "text": "And the surveillance didn&#39;t stop there."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269779.0,
      "end_time": 271476.0,
      "text": "Lyndon Baines Johnson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 271500.0,
      "end_time": 273516.0,
      "text": "during the election campaign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 273540.0,
      "end_time": 279516.0,
      "text": "had the campaign airplane of his rival Barry Goldwater bugged"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279540.0,
      "end_time": 282340.0,
      "text": "as part of his effort to win that election."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 283200.0,
      "end_time": 285700.0,
      "text": "And then, of course, there was Watergate."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 287340.0,
      "end_time": 288796.0,
      "text": "Burglars were caught"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 288820.0,
      "end_time": 291676.0,
      "text": "breaking into the Democratic National Committee headquarters"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 291700.0,
      "end_time": 293236.0,
      "text": "at the Watergate Hotel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 293260.0,
      "end_time": 297436.0,
      "text": "the Nixon administration was involved in covering up the burglary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 297460.0,
      "end_time": 300940.0,
      "text": "and eventually Nixon had to step down as president."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 301860.0,
      "end_time": 306596.0,
      "text": "COINTELPRO and Watergate were a wake-up call for Americans."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 306620.0,
      "end_time": 308476.0,
      "text": "Surveillance was out of control"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308500.0,
      "end_time": 312340.0,
      "text": "and it was being used to squelch political challengers."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 313600.0,
      "end_time": 315596.0,
      "text": "And so Americans rose to the occasion"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 315620.0,
      "end_time": 319600.0,
      "text": "and what we did was we reformed surveillance law."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 319980.0,
      "end_time": 324356.0,
      "text": "And the primary tool we used to reform surveillance law"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 324380.0,
      "end_time": 327760.0,
      "text": "was to require a search warrant"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 327100.0,
      "end_time": 333600.0,
      "text": "for the government to be able to get access to our phone calls and our letters."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 333540.0,
      "end_time": 336396.0,
      "text": "Now, the reason why a search warrant is important"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 336420.0,
      "end_time": 338756.0,
      "text": "is because it interposes a judge"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 338780.0,
      "end_time": 342395.0,
      "text": "in the relationship between investigators and the citizens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 342420.0,
      "end_time": 345396.0,
      "text": "and that judge&#39;s job is to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 345420.0,
      "end_time": 348360.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s good cause for the surveillance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 348600.0,
      "end_time": 351476.0,
      "text": "that the surveillance is targeted at the right people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 351500.0,
      "end_time": 353996.0,
      "text": "and that the information that&#39;s collected"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 354200.0,
      "end_time": 357635.0,
      "text": "is going to be used for legitimate government purposes"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 357660.0,
      "end_time": 360596.0,
      "text": "and not for discriminatory ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 360620.0,
      "end_time": 361836.0,
      "text": "This was our system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 361860.0,
      "end_time": 363116.0,
      "text": "and what this means is"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 363140.0,
      "end_time": 366955.0,
      "text": "that President Obama did not wiretap Trump Tower."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 366980.0,
      "end_time": 371796.0,
      "text": "The system is set up to prevent something like that from happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371820.0,
      "end_time": 373659.0,
      "text": "without a judge being involved."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 374300.0,
      "end_time": 378900.0,
      "text": "But what happens when we&#39;re not talking about phone calls or letters anymore?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 380340.0,
      "end_time": 383360.0,
      "text": "Today, we have technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 383600.0,
      "end_time": 387236.0,
      "text": "that makes it cheap and easy for the government to collect information"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 389940.0,
      "text": "on ordinary everyday people."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 390380.0,
      "end_time": 393760.0,
      "text": "Your phone call records"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 393100.0,
      "end_time": 396716.0,
      "text": "can reveal whether you have an addiction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 396740.0,
      "end_time": 398196.0,
      "text": "what your religion is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 398220.0,
      "end_time": 400876.0,
      "text": "what charities you donate to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 400900.0,
      "end_time": 403380.0,
      "text": "what political candidate you support."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 403860.0,
      "end_time": 407956.0,
      "text": "And yet, our government collected, dragnet-style,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 407980.0,
      "end_time": 410940.0,
      "text": "Americans&#39; calling records for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 412140.0,
      "end_time": 416276.0,
      "text": "In 2012, the Republican National Convention"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 416300.0,
      "end_time": 419676.0,
      "text": "highlighted a new technology it was planning to use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 419700.0,
      "end_time": 421195.0,
      "text": "facial recognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 421220.0,
      "end_time": 424196.0,
      "text": "to identify people who were going to be in the crowd"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 424220.0,
      "end_time": 426676.0,
      "text": "who might be activists or troublemakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 426700.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "and to stop them ahead of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 429200.0,
      "end_time": 432716.0,
      "text": "Today, over 50 percent of American adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 432740.0,
      "end_time": 435140.0,
      "text": "have their faceprint in a government database."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 435740.0,
      "end_time": 439360.0,
      "text": "The Bureau of Alcohol, Tobacco, Firearms and Explosives"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 439600.0,
      "end_time": 440596.0,
      "text": "concocted a plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 440620.0,
      "end_time": 444156.0,
      "text": "to find out what Americans were going to gun shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 444180.0,
      "end_time": 446676.0,
      "text": "by using license plate detectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 446700.0,
      "end_time": 448796.0,
      "text": "to scan the license plates of cars"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 448820.0,
      "end_time": 451600.0,
      "text": "that were in the parking lots of these events."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 451700.0,
      "end_time": 456116.0,
      "text": "Today, we believe that over 70 percent of police departments"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 456140.0,
      "end_time": 459236.0,
      "text": "have automatic license plate detection technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 462700.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re using to track people&#39;s cars as they drive through town."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 463780.0,
      "end_time": 466395.0,
      "text": "And all of this information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 466420.0,
      "end_time": 469356.0,
      "text": "the license plates, the faceprints,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 469380.0,
      "end_time": 470956.0,
      "text": "the phone records,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 470980.0,
      "end_time": 473796.0,
      "text": "your address books, your buddy lists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 473820.0,
      "end_time": 478236.0,
      "text": "the photos that you upload to Dropbox or Google Photos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 478260.0,
      "end_time": 482236.0,
      "text": "and sometimes even your chats and your emails"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 484820.0,
      "text": "are not protected by a warrant requirement."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 485580.0,
      "end_time": 491156.0,
      "text": "So what that means is we have all of this information on regular people"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 491180.0,
      "end_time": 494380.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s newly available at very low expense."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 494860.0,
      "end_time": 496940.0,
      "text": "It is the golden age for surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 498300.0,
      "end_time": 503596.0,
      "text": "Now, every parent is going to understand what this means."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 503620.0,
      "end_time": 505756.0,
      "text": "When you have a little baby"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 505780.0,
      "end_time": 507715.0,
      "text": "and the baby&#39;s young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 507740.0,
      "end_time": 510996.0,
      "text": "that child is not able to climb out of its crib."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 511200.0,
      "end_time": 513915.0,
      "text": "But eventually your little girl gets older"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 513940.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516876.00000000006,
      "text": "and she&#39;s able to climb out of the crib,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 516900.0,
      "end_time": 520675.0,
      "text": "but you tell her, \"Don&#39;t climb out of the crib. OK?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 520700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522876.00000000006,
      "text": "And every parent knows what&#39;s going to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 522900.0,
      "end_time": 525900.0,
      "text": "Some of those babies are going to climb out of the crib."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 526379.0,
      "end_time": 530360.0,
      "text": "Right? That&#39;s the difference between ability and permission."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 530600.0,
      "end_time": 532675.0,
      "text": "Well, the same thing is true with the government today."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 532700.0,
      "end_time": 535475.0,
      "text": "It used to be that our government didn&#39;t have the ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 535499.0,
      "end_time": 539760.0,
      "text": "to do widespread, massive surveillance on hundreds of millions of Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 539100.0,
      "end_time": 540660.0,
      "text": "and then abuse that information."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 541340.0,
      "end_time": 543196.0,
      "text": "But now our government has grown up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 543220.0,
      "end_time": 545180.0,
      "text": "and we have that technology today."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 546200.0,
      "end_time": 548596.0,
      "text": "The government has the ability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 548620.0,
      "end_time": 552196.0,
      "text": "and that means the law is more important than ever before."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 552220.0,
      "end_time": 553956.0,
      "text": "The law is supposed to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 553980.0,
      "end_time": 557996.0,
      "text": "when the government has permission to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 558200.0,
      "end_time": 562156.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s supposed to ensure that there&#39;s some kind of ramification."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 562180.0,
      "end_time": 564675.0,
      "text": "We notice when those laws are broken"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 564700.0,
      "end_time": 567396.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s some of kind of ramification or punishment."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 567420.0,
      "end_time": 570836.0,
      "text": "The law is more important than ever because we are now living in a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 570860.0,
      "end_time": 572956.0,
      "text": "where only rules are stopping the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 572980.0,
      "end_time": 574420.0,
      "text": "from abusing this information."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 574940.0,
      "end_time": 577260.0,
      "text": "But the law has fallen down on the job."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 577660.0,
      "end_time": 581596.0,
      "text": "Particularly since September 11 the law has fallen down on the job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 581620.0,
      "end_time": 584300.0,
      "text": "and we do not have the rules in place that we need."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 585220.0,
      "end_time": 587660.0,
      "text": "And we are seeing the ramifications of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 588200.0,
      "end_time": 591276.0,
      "text": "So fusion centers are these joint task forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 591300.0,
      "end_time": 593596.0,
      "text": "between local, state and federal government"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 593620.0,
      "end_time": 596836.0,
      "text": "that are meant to ferret out domestic terrorism."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 596860.0,
      "end_time": 599356.0,
      "text": "And what we&#39;ve seen is fusion center reports"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 599380.0,
      "end_time": 603156.0,
      "text": "that say that you might be dangerous"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 603180.0,
      "end_time": 606116.0,
      "text": "if you voted for a third-party candidate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 606140.0,
      "end_time": 609316.0,
      "text": "or you own a \"Don&#39;t Tread On Me\" flag,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 609340.0,
      "end_time": 613100.0,
      "text": "or you watched movies that are anti-tax."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 613700.0,
      "end_time": 618476.0,
      "text": "These same fusion centers have spied on Muslim community groups&#39; reading lists"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 618500.0,
      "end_time": 622820.0,
      "text": "and on Quakers who are resisting military recruiting in high schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 624500.0,
      "end_time": 628676.0,
      "text": "The Internal Revenue Service has disproportionately audited"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 628700.0,
      "end_time": 632356.0,
      "text": "groups that have \"Tea Party\" or \"Patriot\" in their name."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 632380.0,
      "end_time": 634956.0,
      "text": "And now customs and border patrol"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 634980.0,
      "end_time": 637756.0,
      "text": "is stopping people as they come into the country"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 637780.0,
      "end_time": 640956.0,
      "text": "and demanding our social networking passwords"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 640980.0,
      "end_time": 643556.0,
      "text": "which will allow them to see who our friends are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 643580.0,
      "end_time": 644796.0,
      "text": "what we say"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 644820.0,
      "end_time": 647540.0,
      "text": "and even to impersonate us online."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 648340.0,
      "end_time": 650996.0,
      "text": "Now, civil libertarians like myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 651200.0,
      "end_time": 655156.0,
      "text": "have been trying to draw people&#39;s attention to these things"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 655180.0,
      "end_time": 657756.0,
      "text": "and fighting against them for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 657780.0,
      "end_time": 661980.0,
      "text": "This was a huge problem during the Obama administration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 662780.0,
      "end_time": 665600.0,
      "text": "but now the problem is worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 666340.0,
      "end_time": 668796.0,
      "text": "When the New York Police Department"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 668820.0,
      "end_time": 670516.0,
      "text": "spies on Muslims"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 670540.0,
      "end_time": 674396.0,
      "text": "or a police department uses license plate detectors"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 674420.0,
      "end_time": 678315.0,
      "text": "to find out where the officers&#39; spouses are"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 678340.0,
      "end_time": 679596.0,
      "text": "or those sorts of things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 679620.0,
      "end_time": 681600.0,
      "text": "that is extremely dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 681740.0,
      "end_time": 684796.0,
      "text": "But when a president repurposes the power"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 684820.0,
      "end_time": 687316.0,
      "text": "of federal surveillance and the federal government"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 687340.0,
      "end_time": 690396.0,
      "text": "to retaliate against political opposition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 690420.0,
      "end_time": 691620.0,
      "text": "that is a tyranny."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 692300.0,
      "end_time": 695620.0,
      "text": "And so we are all activists now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 696460.0,
      "end_time": 699780.0,
      "text": "and we all have something to fear from surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 700580.0,
      "end_time": 704356.0,
      "text": "But just like in the time of Dr. Martin Luther King,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 704380.0,
      "end_time": 706460.0,
      "text": "we can reform the way things are."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 707740.0,
      "end_time": 710140.0,
      "text": "First of all, use encryption."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 710940.0,
      "end_time": 713836.0,
      "text": "Encryption protects your information"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 713860.0,
      "end_time": 718676.0,
      "text": "from being inexpensively and opportunistically collected."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 718700.0,
      "end_time": 721820.0,
      "text": "It rolls back the golden age for surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 723900.0,
      "end_time": 726660.0,
      "text": "Second, support surveillance reform."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 727540.0,
      "end_time": 729716.0,
      "text": "Did you know that if you have a friend"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 729740.0,
      "end_time": 732836.0,
      "text": "who works for the French or German governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 732860.0,
      "end_time": 735996.0,
      "text": "or for an international human rights group"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 736200.0,
      "end_time": 739396.0,
      "text": "or for a global oil company"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 739420.0,
      "end_time": 743380.0,
      "text": "that your friend is a valid foreign intelligence target?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 743740.0,
      "end_time": 747876.0,
      "text": "And what that means is that when you have conversations with that friend,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 747900.0,
      "end_time": 751600.0,
      "text": "the US government may be collecting that information."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 752140.0,
      "end_time": 755396.0,
      "text": "And when that information is collected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 755420.0,
      "end_time": 757596.0,
      "text": "even though it&#39;s conversations with Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 757620.0,
      "end_time": 760716.0,
      "text": "it can then be funneled to the FBI"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 760740.0,
      "end_time": 763196.0,
      "text": "where the FBI is allowed to search through it"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 763220.0,
      "end_time": 764596.0,
      "text": "without getting a warrant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 764620.0,
      "end_time": 766276.0,
      "text": "without probable cause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 766300.0,
      "end_time": 768516.0,
      "text": "looking for information about Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 768540.0,
      "end_time": 771956.0,
      "text": "and whatever crimes we may have committed"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 771980.0,
      "end_time": 775200.0,
      "text": "with no need to document any kind of suspicion."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 775740.0,
      "end_time": 778716.0,
      "text": "The law that allows some of this to happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 778740.0,
      "end_time": 782836.0,
      "text": "is called Section 702 of the FISA Amendments Act,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 782860.0,
      "end_time": 785396.0,
      "text": "and we have a great opportunity this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 785420.0,
      "end_time": 790156.0,
      "text": "because Section 702 is going to expire at the end of 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 790180.0,
      "end_time": 794795.0,
      "text": "which means that Congress&#39;s inertia is on our side"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 794820.0,
      "end_time": 796396.0,
      "text": "if we want reform."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 796420.0,
      "end_time": 800116.0,
      "text": "And we can pressure our representatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 800140.0,
      "end_time": 803636.0,
      "text": "to actually implement important reforms to this law"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 803660.0,
      "end_time": 807200.0,
      "text": "and protect our data from this redirection and misuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 808380.0,
      "end_time": 813396.0,
      "text": "And finally, one of the reasons why things have gotten so out of control"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 813420.0,
      "end_time": 816315.0,
      "text": "is because so much of what happens with surveillance --"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 816340.0,
      "end_time": 820876.0,
      "text": "the technology, the enabling rules and the policies"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 820900.0,
      "end_time": 824476.0,
      "text": "that are either there or not there to protect us --"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 824500.0,
      "end_time": 826916.0,
      "text": "are secret or classified."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 826940.0,
      "end_time": 831156.0,
      "text": "We need transparency, and we need to know as Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 831180.0,
      "end_time": 833715.0,
      "text": "what the government is doing in our name"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 833740.0,
      "end_time": 838316.0,
      "text": "so that the surveillance that takes place and the use of that information"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 838340.0,
      "end_time": 840820.0,
      "text": "is democratically accounted for."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 842220.0,
      "end_time": 844316.0,
      "text": "We are all activists now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 844340.0,
      "end_time": 847980.0,
      "text": "which means that we all have something to worry about from surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 848540.0,
      "end_time": 851956.0,
      "text": "But like in the time of Dr. Martin Luther King,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 851980.0,
      "end_time": 854276.0,
      "text": "there is stuff that we can do about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 854300.0,
      "end_time": 858219.0,
      "text": "So please join me, and let&#39;s get to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 858820.0,
      "end_time": 860360.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 860600.0,
      "end_time": 863819.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}